{"tid":1104041,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Excel 多條件範圍判定格式化重複的值 [問題]","createTime":"2019-04-12T22:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T15:34:30.000Z","uid":14889,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dab645b713ce2285b25218189ac59afc2bd371ee","tid":1104041,"uid":14889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T22:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QW79Tn9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQW79Tn9.png&h=6b943944&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nG 列填入 1 字 ; 同行 I:M 會變<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色</span><br />\nG 列填入 2 字 ; 同行 I:M 會變<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色</span><br />\n<br />\n依家想做既效果係 當 G 行填入 2 字既時候<br />\nI:M 同行紅色既數值，要判定如果有上下紅色範圍有重複的值就另外格式化 Highlighted<br />\n例如上圖 G9, G10, G16 填入 2 字<br />\n同行 I9:M9 , I10 :M10 , I16:M16 上下比對有無重複<br />\nI9 同 I16 都係16 (即重複) <br />\n想重複左就該格 或者 該行(I:M) 用其他顏色高亮顯示<br />\n自己淨係識用countif($I$3:$M$42,I3)&gt;1 驗證重複<br />\n不過做唔到加個判決係 G 行係2 就用同行既I:M 做判定重複<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8285d85819ce5e696139f1d1792a99b711b94c5a","tid":1104041,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T23:01:42.000Z","msg":"If?"},{"pid":"9bf859bc113a3f78b8922d9143cb1421f0b8c08d","tid":1104041,"uid":191623,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T00:15:45.000Z","msg":"你現有conditional formatting嘅formula應該係：<br />\n一、黃色<br />\n=$G3=1<br />\n二、紅色<br />\n=$G3=2<br />\n<br />\n你只需要喺兩個conditions<ins><strong>上面</strong></ins>加多一個condition<br />\n=AND($G3=2,COUNTIFS($G$3:$G$<span style=\"color: blue;\">9999</span>,2,I$3:I$<span style=\"color: blue;\">9999</span>,I3)&gt;1)<br />\n<br />\n同埋記住喺呢個condition度剔「Stop if True」個check box<br />\n<br />\n不過呢個condition只會highlight重複嗰一格，要highlight成行有啲難度，唔想諗"},{"pid":"b7ff077cfffea61efdda8d4fa94a3a71f153da2c","tid":1104041,"uid":14889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"